### ============================================================
### Catalog — Published Items
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Auth required for all endpoints (use Bearer token).
### Returns only published products (Catalog BC view).
### For anonymous product browsing see: GET /api/storefront/products
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "aDminN@W25!"
}

###

# ============================================================
# ITEMS — published products (authenticated)
# ============================================================

### Get all published items — paged
# Expected: 200 OK  →  ProductListVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?pageSize=10&pageNo=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get published items — search
# Expected: 200 OK  →  filtered list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?searchString=laptop&pageSize=5&pageNo=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get published items — next page
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?pageSize=5&pageNo=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get item by id
# Expected: 200 OK  →  ProductDetailsVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get item — not found
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###
